<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>getTimezoneFromString() assumes that all timezone offsets are between -12 and +12. However, there are several timezones with an offset greater than that, such as New Zealand DST (UTC+13) and Pacific/Kiritimati (UTC+14).</p>

<p>Test case:
{quote}
$a = new Zend_Date();
var_dump($a-&gt;getTimezoneFromString('18:00:00+1300'));
{quote}
Output: string(3) "UTC"
Expected output: string(10) "Etc/GMT-13"</p>

